{"tid":1610251,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【突發】黨鐵: 部分車站有可能未能在明日恢復服務","createTime":"2019-10-01T16:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T19:51:48.000Z","uid":89184,"like":51,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"20aa80a5096f137344a969b7a18bce0fd91761ce","tid":1610251,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:50:03.000Z","msg":"// 港鐵發聲明，表示在今日（10月1日）各區的公眾活動中，超過20個港鐵車站的設施被示威者蓄意破壞及縱火，乘客、港鐵員工及鐵路安全受嚴重影響。港鐵強調縱火行為可引致十分嚴重後果，對此極度憤慨，強烈譴責這些罔顧乘客及港鐵員工安全的非法行為；又稱工程人員需於晚上收車後修復受損設施，部分車站或設施有可能未能在明日（2日）恢復服務。 //<br />\n<br />\n咁大家記得聽日可能冇車返工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左唔好令香港人罷課成功, 下次記得千其唔好搞黨鐵啦!!"},{"pid":"fc24df11d539de1bb6bcbb1be95c67312e8f0b1f","tid":1610251,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:50:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cdc299abb48cff6a14e8a19dabe5e9a398771e4e","tid":1610251,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:50:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d6604cd3e435295c1de50defbd3548cf5bacd77","tid":1610251,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:50:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b6665cda879c603c34ab4f60c8ca53bb2cd622f","tid":1610251,"uid":45914,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:51:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ea2b834b51770511f728988813190f24a663b92","tid":1610251,"uid":53610,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:52:00.000Z","msg":"咁開心聽日實去賀一賀黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0568c21840ad19e4a35de5d7b7dcdbecc0970ac","tid":1610251,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:52:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ec54c45c5787530fc3a93ce8d2d96a05edc155ea","tid":1610251,"uid":11563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"20aa80a5096f137344a969b7a18bce0fd91761ce","tid":1610251,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco