"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:54:54.000Z","msg":"快d整個list出黎睇下邊到開到"},{"pid":"415bb539d3575e581e77ce8945c27ae692c996b8","tid":1610251,"uid":169665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:56:37.000Z","msg":"講啦，次次第二朝都開得返，除左831"},{"pid":"5560306de2d91378f7bd8665f12c1209e6293db0","tid":1610251,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:57:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呵欠</span></strong>"},{"pid":"cbdee9f4c4ce776dc6daaa59fb9774b31c8fea5c","tid":1610251,"uid":136233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:58:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19208b268364c39c30d5e6f76ed4bcdbe481558e","tid":1610251,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb5da2dba9cc7d179d988152255c552ccf3fac5","tid":1610251,"uid":52609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:58:55.000Z","msg":"次次都係咁講，同埋一早封左站，入面邊有損傷呀"},{"pid":"3aa39500ccfba1cd2acd708271b413d38bc1bd67","tid":1610251,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:59:58.000Z","msg":"工程人員罷工啦屌"},{"pid":"bd55681621fd03c019b84738571bd61f24db0d06","tid":1610251,"uid":244876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:01:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />樹窿再次歡迎大家加入<br />\n知道過去兩個月，大家既生活都過得好壓抑。有人係依兩個月之間同父母嗌大交，同伴侶分手，同朋友斷交，有人晚晚夜歸，有人用到無哂錢。或者你覺得好迷惘好無奈，或者你覺得無岀路。有見及此，開左個谷俾大家入黎吐下苦水，只談現實，不談夢境。希望大家可以舒發下，減減壓，然後大家一齊繼續向前行。<br />\n<br />\n發緊想發未發就發夢都唔好係公海講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n保障大家安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講明先 係歡迎任何人講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n理得你藍定黃 狗定人 貓定兔<br />\n我地好希望大家可以有個好始既渠道釋放咁耐以來既情緒<br />\n如果大家有朋友仔想入來無任歡迎咖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋記得不指責不要質問 任何指責及質問均無助大家發洩情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FE2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw&d=0svHhEbJ%2FFd80Myex1SsDQNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=c20d2ffc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/E2OHoFZRBnlI3qIuGfFikw</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無論你係邊一到，保護自己，不要透露個人資料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d98a9f0f7e3e7c05a7fa3b99e135fdd7d9563d","tid":1610251,"uid":294302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:02:19.000Z","msg":"開賭局 除左太子兩個出口<br />\n其他如常"},{"pid":"33d02b283827b9b3d12e0021999d9b42f29544f0","tid":1610251,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:03:06.000Z","msg":"其實今日黨鐵封站有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到百花齊放<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba5b86aa877095f72f90eb95368c250b23bb0b63","tid":1610251,"uid":42629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:03:25.000Z","msg":"樓主岩岩出冊?<br />\n個個禮拜日都係咁講"}]}